nodes.text: Star Wars Omnibus: Dark Times Volume 1

Omnibus: Dark Times Volume 1 is an Star Wars Omnibus-series trade paperback collecting the final two issues of the Star Wars: Republic comic book series, the first three story arcs of the Star Wars: Dark Times comic book series, and the prologue issue of the Star Wars: Dark Times: Blue Harvest arc. It was published on December 31, 2013.

Master Dass Jennir will strive to find out what it means to be a Jedi in a changed galaxy now ruled by the Empire. Master K'Kruhk—suddenly responsible for a group of Jedi younglings—will sacrifice much for their safety. The struggles of the Jedi will intertwine with those of others now living in fear, including the diverse crew of a smuggling ship, the Uhumele, and a Nosaurian whose troubles begin when the Clone Wars end.
